      "description": "$4,300 - Honest project-grade car being sold in poor condition. It shows heavy wear inside and out, with noticeable cosmetic issues to the body, paint, trim, and interior, and it should be expected to need significant mechanical sorting and deferred maintenance. This is not a clean driver or a lightly used example \u2014 it\u2019s best suited for someone looking for a budget fixer-upper, restoration project, or parts donor. If you come expecting a rough, tired car that will need work, you\u2019ll be looking at it correctly.",
