      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle is a great opportunity for a value-minded buyer who needs basic transportation or wants a solid project at an accessible price point. It shows its age and is best suited for someone who appreciates a budget-friendly option with plenty of potential. Priced to reflect its condition while still offering real utility, this is a practical choice for the right owner.",
