    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of potential? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great budget-friendly option for someone who wants basic transportation, a project, or a handy spare vehicle. It\u2019s being sold honestly as-is, and with a little TLC it could make a really worthwhile buy for the right person. If you appreciate a straightforward deal and don\u2019t mind giving a car some love, this one could be a great fit.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget project or runaround with strong enthusiast potential. This car shows its age cosmetically, but the powertrain pulls through the rev range, the transmission engages as it should, and it remains a usable platform for someone who knows their way around basic maintenance. Good candidate for a commuter, parts donor, or restoration-minded buyer looking for an affordable entry point. Priced to move and worth a look if you want mechanical value over cosmetics.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Honest beater with plenty of life for the right buyer. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Turn heads and spark ideas with this honest, full-of-character ride that wears its story proudly. It\u2019s the kind of car that appeals to someone who sees potential where others see a project\u2014a great canvas for a weekend tinkerer, budget-minded driver, or anyone hunting for an affordable set of wheels with personality. It has that unmistakable lived-in charm, the kind that makes every trip feel a little more real, a little less ordinary. If you want something flashy and forgettable, keep scrolling. If you want value, presence, and the chance to make it your own, this one deserves a look.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
